===Noun===
{{head|mch|noun}}
# A non-[[indigenous]] person, [[Creole]], sometimes in particular a [[benevolent]] [[Spanish]]-speaking [[settler]] in contrast with the [[malevolent]] {{m|mch|jañudu}}.
